		<body>
			<pb n="1R"/>
				<p rend="align(right)"><placeName><sic>Pittsburg</sic></placeName> <date>Janry 18d 1850</date></p>
				<p><addressee>Rev I. Leeser</addressee></p>
			<p rend="indent(2)">Reverend Sir</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">Within I send you three<lb/> Dollars for the last year <sic>subscribtion</sic> for your valuable<lb/> <sic>Occitent</sic>.</p>
			<p rend="indent(1)"><sic>through</sic> this opportunity I will address to you<lb/> a few <sic>worts</sic> respecting our holy <date>Sabbat</date> &#38; the <date>Sabbath</date> law<lb/> I have several times noticed in our Occ. your <sic>complaind</sic><lb/> against the unjustness of the <date>Sabbath</date> Laws <sic>wich</sic> exist<lb/> in this and in autre States&#44; in your last number<lb/> for <date>Dec</date>&#44; you have an article&#44; the <date>Sabbath</date> Laws of<lb/> <placeName>Virginia</placeName> lately passed by that Legislator <sic>wich</sic> you<lb/> justly pruised<add>&#63;</add> so much&#59; Now sir I ask would it<lb/> not be advisable for the Israelites of this Nati to<lb/> petition our Legislator to pass such a law similar<lb/> to thos passed already in <placeName>Virginia</placeName> and <placeName>Ohio</placeName>&#44; concerning<lb/> those who keep the seventh day as their <date>Sabbath</date>.</p>
				<p>I believe in my humble Opinion if the Jews of this State<lb/> would get up a Petition to be Started in <placeName>Philadelphia</placeName><lb/> &#40;as there are the most of our Brethren in this State&#41; a good<lb/> many Christians would sign it also and if it should<lb/> pass it would do more good to our Religion than any<lb/> thing else I could think of.  As for instance there are<lb/> here in <placeName><sic>Pittsburg</sic></placeName> twenty five Jewish Families&#44; all<lb/> as I think in limited circumstances among them only two<lb/> that keep <date>Sabbath</date> because they say we can not <sic>provid</sic> in</p>
			<pb n="1V"/>
				<p>five days for seven&#44; now should such a Petition to be got<lb/> up and pass so that we Jews could <sic>attent</sic> to our <sic>Buissness</sic><lb/> on <date>Sunday</date> the most part if not all would keep <date>sabbath</date><lb/> and by this means would become more attached to their<lb/> holy Religion and I <sic>darsey</sic> it is so through the<lb/> whole State <sic>wher</sic> there any Jews residing</p>
				<p>We <sic>hav</sic> here a temporary <sic>Sinagog</sic> a <sic>bureing</sic> Ground<lb/> a <hi rend="underline">Halan</hi> &#38; <hi rend="underline">Shochel</hi> but hard work to get <hi rend="underline">minian</hi><lb/> of a <date>Sabbath</date> as the most of them are <sic>attenting</sic> to their<lb/> <sic>Buissness</sic>&#44; to try it at least would do no harm</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">with very much resepct I am</p>
			<p rend="indent(3)">yours truly</p>
			<p rend="indent(5)"><persName role="author">N. Gallinger</persName></p>
				<p>N.B. you must forgive my<lb/> <sic>uncorect</sic> writing &#38; spelling as i am no <sic>schollar</sic></p>
			<pb n="2V"/>
